// R6 — Claim extraction worker (refactored through OracleAIClient + staging).
//
// Spec compliance:
//   - docs/oracle/05-ai-retrofit-phase-packet.md Phase R6
//   - docs/oracle/03-candidate-before-claim-validation.md
